# VEHICLE::SET_CARGOBOB_PICKUP_MAGNET_FALLOFF

## Summary
Set how the force magnitude drops off as the distance to the entity increases while the entity is being picked up

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** cargobob
* **FLOAT** magnetFalloff
